Wizards: Give them items and equipment that will help them make their spells stick more<BR>
<BR>
And when Norrath gets bigger, give everyone a self port ability to their guild or like with the newbie equipment, give them stones like the nexus stones that can teleport them to their guild when they stand in a nexus (though make it so you can't hold a guild stone and a nexus stone at once.<BR>
<BR>
That's all I have to add Whew<BR>
